OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA drier and brighter day to
OL,6,Fcome compared to Saturday with the
OL,7,Fbest of the brightness during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Cloud will increase later
OL,9,Fwith some spots of rain arriving in
OL,10,Fthe west later. Feeling a little
OL,11,Fwarmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA largely dry evening, but
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain will gradually
OL,15,Fspread eastwards overnight. The rain
OL,16,Fturning heavier and more persistent by
OL,17,Fdawn. A breezy but mild night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
